g_searchEnginePlainTextArray['c994843e75c10c9845703e105c7d94ff'] = 'Description IIH Essentials offers a debugging view for experienced users. It provides additional information in the event of an error and can help with troubleshooting. It shows information that is relevant to Support personnel, such as component versions and live logs. Extended logging can be enabled on a functional basis to obtain detailed information when needed. The debugging view can be accessed at \"https://\u003cIED_IP\u003e/iih-essentials/#/debug\". The recording of log data requires the creation of a  log variable . The user interface of the debugging view is divided into the following areas: (1) Information area: Frontend version Backend version (2) Enable/disable debugging mode (3) Log settings, enable/disable individual logs (4) Log view';
